home.title: Git-based CMS
home.desc: Static is a Git-based CMS for bootstrapping landing sites for open-source projects. By utilizing Vue.js, Nuxt.js and Vuetify, all of the heavy lifting is done for you - no coding skills required. Just focus on showing off your project and all that it has to offer.
